@baseUrl = http://localhost:8081
# ⚠️ REPLACE THE VALUE BELOW WITH A JSESSIONID CREATED BY THIS SAME BACKEND (localhost:8081) ⚠️
# Tip: sign in via http://localhost:5173 after setting VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8081,
# then copy JSESSIONID from browser devtools for localhost.
@cookie = JSESSIONID=FDD853B730F83611BEB67B3DD2F6A0F6

### ==========================================
### MODULE 1: AUTHENTICATION
### ==========================================

### 1.1 Get Current Logged-In User
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Cookie: {{cookie}}


### ==========================================
### MODULE 2: BOOKINGS
### ==========================================

### 2.1 Create a Booking
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings
Cookie: {{cookie}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "PAF Group Meeting",
  "resource": "Library Room A",
  "purpose": "Group Assignment Meeting",
  "expectedAttendees": 4,
  "startTime": "2026-04-25T09:00:00",
  "endTime": "2026-04-25T11:00:00"
}

### 2.2 Get My Bookings
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/me
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### 2.3 Approve a Booking (Admin Only)
# Note: Ensure booking ID '1' exists.
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/bookings/1/approve
Cookie: {{cookie}}


### ==========================================
### MODULE 3: TICKETS & COMMENTS
### ==========================================

### 3.1 Create a Maintenance Ticket
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tickets
Cookie: {{cookie}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundaryXYZ

------FormBoundaryXYZ
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="subject"

Broken AC in Library
------FormBoundaryXYZ
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

The air conditioner on the second floor is leaking.
------FormBoundaryXYZ
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="resource"

Library 2nd Floor
------FormBoundaryXYZ
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="category"

HVAC
------FormBoundaryXYZ
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="priority"

HIGH
------FormBoundaryXYZ--

### 3.2 Add a Comment to the Ticket
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tickets/1/comments
Cookie: {{cookie}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Technician has been notified and is on the way."
}

### 3.3 Update Ticket Status (Technician/Admin)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/tickets/1/status
Cookie: {{cookie}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS"
}


### ==========================================
### MODULE 4: NOTIFICATIONS (Member 4 specific)
### ==========================================

### 4.1 Get Unread Notification Count
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/my/unread-count
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### 4.2 Get All My Notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/my
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### 4.3 Mark All Notifications as Read
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/my/read-all
Cookie: {{cookie}}


### ==========================================
### MODULE 5: RESOURCES
### ==========================================

### 5.1 Get All Resources
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/resources
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### 5.2 Create a Resource (Admin Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/resources
Cookie: {{cookie}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New Advanced Computing Lab",
  "type": "LAB",
  "capacity": 30,
  "location": "Engineering Building - Floor 3",
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "description": "High performance computing lab equipped with latest GPUs."
}

### 5.3 Get Resource by ID
# Note: Ensure resource ID '1' exists.
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/resources/1
Cookie: {{cookie}}


### ==========================================
### EXTRA ADMIN TESTS
### ==========================================

### List All Tickets (Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tickets
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### List All Bookings (Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/bookings
Cookie: {{cookie}}
